, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional day\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"Federer\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wimbledon final\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later, he defeated Juan Martin del Potro to become the first player, male or female, to win two Olympic singles golds.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999968215657226, \"rank\": 3.1684117710112855e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first player\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"female\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympic singles golds\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray also led Britain to the Davis Cup title in 2015, the country's first in 79 years.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0177507264102436e-49, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.99944278613214, \"rank\": 0.0005525318690093624, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Davis Cup title\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"79 years\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has won 46 titles in all and banked around $65 million in